219:**Amazon Transcribe Medical as an alternative or complement to HealthScribe.** Transcribe Medical is AWS's medical-specific ASR service. It supports both batch and streaming transcription with medical vocabulary tuning and specialty-specific models (primary care, cardiology, oncology, radiology, neurology, urology). Teams that want more control over the pipeline (e.g., custom diarization, custom note-generation prompts, integration with a non-HealthScribe generation step) use Transcribe Medical as the ASR building block and assemble the downstream pipeline themselves. Teams that want the managed end-to-end path use HealthScribe and accept its opinions about diarization and note structure.
